                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "简述",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "岩王帝君",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "岩之魔神。归终与之交好，定下盟约。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "现在以凡人",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "钟离",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "的身份生活。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 2523,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/06/19/47826599/46ee1323ddfe94fe1707c1d50912504e_1907085798915618877.png",
                      "name": "留云借风真君",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "和归终一样精通机关术的仙人。据说岩王帝君曾评价归终的机关更优秀。 (*1)",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "歌尘浪市真君",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "又名萍姥姥。她曾与归终争论机关和作曲的问题。 (*1)",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "马科修斯",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "炉灶之魔神。他是归终的朋友之一，也常被邀请到她家作客。 (*2)",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "现在以香菱取的名字",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "锅巴",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "生活。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "right",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "*注1：来自剧情预告-「余音萦心」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "right",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "*注2：来自「磬弦奏华夜」的活动剧情",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
